FBIS4-36156 "drnes109_j_94009" FBIS-NES-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Radio Reports Successes of Southern Forces Aden Radio Reports Successes of Southern Forces North's Assault on Shabwah Repulsed EA0606185594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 6 Jun 94 EA0606185594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 6 Jun 94 English BFN [Text] A military communique released by the [word indistinct] command in Shabwah Governorate mentioned that the Armed Forces of the DRY [Democratic Republic of Yemen], supported by the masses and tribes, are repelling the attacks carried out by the Sanaa regime. The communique said that the Armed Forces of the DRY during the last few days inflicted on the (?launching) force and destroyed seven tanks, four artillery sets, and three Katyusha vehicles. There were 65 killed and more than 200 injured.
